            <text>
                <body>
                <div>
                    <head><title>Donaci&#243; de dotze castells en feu a Bernat At&#243; IV pel comte Ramon Berenguer III</title></head>
                    <dateline>s. d. [1112, juny 9]</dateline>
                    <p> </p>
                    <p>En compliment de l&#8217;acord signat el dia anterior, el comte Ramon Berenguer III de Barcelona d&#243;na en feu a Bernat At&#243; IV, vescomte de Besiers, els dotze castells que n&#8217;ha rebut en alou.</p>
                    <p>========================================================================</p>
                    <div><p><note n="a">B avantposa la r&#250;brica <hi rend="italic">Donatio quam fecit Raimundus, comes Barcinonensis, Bernardo Atonis super duodecim castellis Carcassonae</hi>.</note>Ego <persName xml:id="p1" key="Ramon Berenguer III el Gran" role="donador">Raimundus Berengarii, Barchinonensis comes</persName>, dono ad fevum tibi <persName xml:id="p2" key="Bernat At&#243; IV de Besiers" role="beneficiari">Bernardo Atonis, Biterrensi vicecomiti</persName>, <placeName xml:id="pl1" key="Boisseson, castell">Boxazon</placeName>,<note n="b"><hi rend="italic">Boxahonem</hi> D.</note> <placeName xml:id="pl2" key="R&#242;caceri&#232;ra, castell" type="castell">Roccam Cedam</placeName>,<note n="c"><hi rend="italic">Rocham Cezieram</hi> D; <hi rend="italic">Rocham Cedenam</hi> E.</note> <placeName xml:id="pl3" key="Ambialet, castell">Ambiletum</placeName>, <placeName xml:id="pl4" key="Curvala, castell">Curvallem</placeName>, <placeName xml:id="pl5" key="Cailar, Lo, castell"><hi rend="italic">Castlar</hi></placeName>, <placeName xml:id="pl6" key="Pesen&#224;s, castell i vila"><hi rend="italic">Pedenaz</hi></placeName>, <placeName xml:id="pl7" key="Cast&#232;ln&#242;u" type="castell">Castellum Novum</placeName>, <placeName xml:id="pl8" key="Mesa, castell">Messoam</placeName>, <placeName xml:id="pl9" key="Sant Pon&#231; de Mauchins, castell" type="castell">Castellum Sancti Poncii</placeName>, <placeName xml:id="pl10" key="Poget, Lo, castell">Poietum</placeName>, <placeName xml:id="pl11" key="Mercoirol, castell"><hi rend="italic">Mercoirol</hi></placeName> et <placeName xml:id="pl12" key="Cauvi&#231;on, castell">Calvitionem</placeName>,<note n="d"><hi rend="italic">Calumcionem</hi> D.</note> quod reddas illos mihi quando ego illos<note n="e"><hi rend="italic">illos</hi> om&#232;s E i HGL.</note> tibi requiram per me aut per meum missum et quod<note n="f"><hi rend="italic">aut</hi> HGL.</note> servias illos mihi.</p></div>
